com.viaoa.hub

Class HubChangeListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.hub.HubChangeListener

  • public abstract class HubChangeListener
extends Object
    Allows listening for changes to 1 or more Hubs and property paths. Can include compare values, that can then be checked using getValue() to see if all conditions are true. Use add method to add as many checks and hubs as necessary. calling getValue will determine if all of the conditions are true. ex: AO != null, editQueryEnabled=true, propValue==X, etc.
    Author:
    vincevia
